answer: Dear students, a Mock Interview will be conducted from week 10 until week 14 to prepare UTM students with job interview skills in an environment similar to an actual job interview. It will be conducted by several slots based on the faculties which will be assigned later. The selected dates for Mock Interview are as follow: 14th May 2024, 21st May 2024, 28th May 2024, 11th June 2024. Further information regarding Mock Interview will be released in near time. ⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️ It is compulsory to complete all the assignments because it ensures you for a mock interview with the same base knowledge and you’re ready to hit the ground running from day one. Assignments must be completed *before 11:59 pm, 20th April 2024*.
